Skills.Name: Take Some Treats...
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Raises EVA of first ally in line by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s if Yellow Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of single ally. Raises EVA of first ally in line if Yellow Elemental

Skills.Name: Puppet Master
Skills.Description: Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color>) on single enemy with highest ATK. Further lowers ACC by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 5s if Blue Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 3-hit DMG on single enemy, lowers ACC if Blue Elemental

Skills.Name: Candy Rain
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 30s if Yellow Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies, raises ATK if Yellow Elemental

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription:
Recovers HP of all allies,
inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Lazy Vampire
Skills.Description: Each time DMG is inflicted, inflicts Dark on single random enemy for 2s. Further raises DMG Received for single random enemy by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 7s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time DMG is inflicted, inflicts Dark on single random enemy, raises DMG Received for single random enemy
